e-smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">Janelle Monáe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nothing-but-thieves">Nothing But Thieves</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-odell">Tom Odell</a>等乐队的表演。请在此处查看<em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/mad-cool-festival-2024-day-one-photos-dua-lipa-janelle-monae-smashing-pumpkins-3773899">对今年音乐节的综述</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mad-cool-festival-2025-olivia-rodrigo-kings-of-leon-and-noah-kahan-lead-stacked-first-line-up-3823842">Mad Cool Festival 2025 后：Olivia Rodrigo、Kings Of Leon 和 Noah Kahan 领衔首发阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
